snippet.textDisplay: Singers ( both Odia and Tamil) have ofcourse delivered the song so beautifully...the best Odia song ever fusion with a lovely Tamil rap sequence. "BANDE TAMILNADU"  One thing I noticed, many people from India and abroad loved the music even though they do not understand the language...it says just one thing..there are still many more people those who appreciate others than those who do not. Ms Mohapatra and team..please keep singing Odiya songs..please do not get dishearten by all the negative comments you received from some of the selfish people from Odissa..there number is just a handful..you are one of the few those who love Odissa truly. You should meet Ritesh Agarwala..OYO innovator...one more genius from a small town of Odisha.
